# AI Rules: Folder-Based SDLC
Scope: Actions limited to folder purpose. Incremental updates only. No rewrites.

- /Ideas: Concept-only. Lightweight notes/sketches. Tag unknowns. List next steps.
- /PM: Structured requirements. Convert Ideas to Tasks. Track dependencies/risks. 
- /Dev: Production-code focus. Minimal changes. Update docs for API/logic shifts.
- /QA: Test vs PRD. Log bugs (Steps/Expected/Actual). Traceability to PM tasks.

Handoff: Ideas -> PM (Validate) -> Dev (Implement) -> QA (Verify) -> PM (Status).
Done: Ideas=Clear | PM=Testable | Dev=Tests Pass | QA=Verified.